COMMERCIAL USE

Any commercial use — including operating this adapter as part of a plant,
machine, production line or paid service — requires a commercial license key
issued per machine. Contact https://github.com/gokturk413 with the machine's
Hardware ID (shown by the adapter's "Check License" button) to obtain one.

NATIVE ENGINE

The native protocol engine binaries (the iobroker.rockwell_ethernetip-<platform>
npm packages) are proprietary components of this product. They are licensed for
use solely together with this adapter and enforce the license key at runtime.
Reverse engineering, decompilation or redistribution outside the npm packages
is not permitted.

